{"tid":1740993,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該你班學生放飯唔好講發夢野","createTime":"2019-11-20T06:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T12:13:07.000Z","uid":148406,"like":157,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd3124bdf6ea0440b39ad01381bd70cf455b6d1","tid":1740993,"uid":148406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:54:52.000Z","msg":"講過幾多次<br />\n發夢既內容唔可以亂咁講<br />\n點解頭先食飯仲俾我聽到同枱幾個中學生係到高談闊論大冒險<br />\n<br />\n即使上一秒我同朋友係到屌警狗屌得幾大聲都好<br />\n唔代表我地係自己人<br />\n如果同枱既唔係我而係藍絲<br />\n你地連鋪頭門口都未必行到出去<br />\n已經講過好多次啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">發夢野唔好係出面講</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">發夢野唔好係出面講</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">發夢野唔好係出面講</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n知唔知除左自己, 你仲會害埋其他手足<br />\n係街上面除左自己識既人之外<br />\n要當所有人都係共匪奸細<br />\n我地打緊仗架!!<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾我再聽到有下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">PS 我本來見你地著校服已經想請你地食飯<br />\n見你講得咁大聲我唯有收返埋個銀包<br />\n下次見到面既 <br />\n講句「光復香港」<br />\n我會答你「時代革命」<br />\n再請你地去食好野</span>"},{"pid":"e455f4e1d86881f445fd6dbe90f4c70afd7dff6f","tid":1740993,"uid":140737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d1b76903af993108318c706f497a847b80191c","tid":1740993,"uid":139677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:00:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d2e901b9e2444d516306efe1d61fc08e9260d70","tid":1740993,"uid":148406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:02:36.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8066464790bc0eb793ca3ef36ecbb509abf698fd","tid":1740993,"uid":243854,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":